{"body": "The correct benchmark would be\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nrequire 'benchmark'\r\n\r\nn = 100000\r\n\r\nBenchmark.bmbm do |x|\r\n  x.report(:===) { n.times { 'a' === String } }\r\n  x.report(:is_a?) { n.times { 'a'.is_a?(String) } }\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\n`is_a?` still turns to be a bit faster though.\r\n\r\n```\r\nRehearsal -----------------------------------------\r\n===     0.040000   0.000000   0.040000 (  0.049118)\r\nis_a?   0.030000   0.000000   0.030000 (  0.022938)\r\n-------------------------------- total: 0.070000sec\r\n\r\n            user     system      total        real\r\n===     0.020000   0.000000   0.020000 (  0.025311)\r\nis_a?   0.020000   0.000000   0.020000 (  0.017198)\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/18969662", "created_at": "2013-06-05T11:25:28Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10852#issuecomment-18969662", "updated_at": "2013-06-05T11:25:28Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10852, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/goshakkk", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/477dc65c2083c0aea87485b399372db0?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F8e6fe8f267d3b31fe2e5b5da1787a120.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/received_events", "gravatar_id": "477dc65c2083c0aea87485b399372db0", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "goshakkk", "type": "User", "id": 315596, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goshakkk/followers"}, "owner": "r